	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe one easy way would be to use a larger ROM, and hook the upper address lines to a dip switch.  That way you could run several games that use the same board and hardware.  I think the games you listed all use different boards though.
<br />
<br />Otherwise you'll have to code a menu and hack the games, is that what you were planning on doing already?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


